test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [] == [[93], [93], [93], [93]]
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: [93]
  Full diff:
  - [[93], [93], [93], [93]]
  + []
test_list_of_single_number:
assert [] == [[93]]
  Right contains one more item: [93]
  Full diff:
  - [[93]]
  + []
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 804357 == 93
 +  where 804357 = <built-in function prod>([1, 3, 31, 93, 1, 3, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
